cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.HC 

The paper focuses on analyzing the limitations of deep neural networks in image classification tasks, specifically in understanding the relatedness between object classes. This falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. The paper also uses methods inspired by cognitive psychology (cs.HC) to conduct experiments and analyze the learning behavior of DNNs. Additionally, the paper discusses the tendency and limitations of DNNs, which falls under the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and neural networks (cs.NE) sub-categories.
